  {"word":"illicit","pos":"adj","ja":"違法な、不正な","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪˈlɪsɪt","ex":"Police seized a large shipment of illicit drugs.","exJa":"警察は違法薬物の大量出荷を押収した。","collocations":["illicit drugs","illicit trade"],"synonyms":["illegal","unlawful"],"distractorHint":["合法の","内密の","高価な"]},
