  {"word":"incongruous","pos":"adj","ja":"場違いな、不調和な","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪnˈkɒŋgruəs","ex":"His casual outfit seemed incongruous at the formal event.","exJa":"彼のカジュアルな服装は正式な場に場違いだった。","collocations":["seem incongruous","incongruous with"],"synonyms":["inconsistent","out of place"],"distractorHint":["調和した","一般的な","目立たない"]},
  {"word":"indelible","pos":"adj","ja":"消せない、忘れられない","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪnˈdɛlɪbəl","ex":"The trip left an indelible impression on all of us.","exJa":"その旅行は私たち全員に忘れられない印象を残した。","collocations":["indelible mark","indelible memory"],"synonyms":["permanent","unforgettable"],"distractorHint":["一時的な","曖昧な","楽しい"]},
  {"word":"indispensable","pos":"adj","ja":"不可欠な","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ˌɪndɪˈspɛnsəbəl","ex":"Clean water is indispensable for human survival.","exJa":"清潔な水は人間の生存に不可欠だ。","collocations":["indispensable tool","prove indispensable"],"synonyms":["essential","vital"],"distractorHint":["不要な","贅沢な","代替可能な"]},
  {"word":"inept","pos":"adj","ja":"無能な、下手な","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪˈnɛpt","ex":"He was surprisingly inept at handling simple customer complaints.","exJa":"彼は簡単な顧客対応にも意外なほど無能だった。","collocations":["inept at","hopelessly inept"],"synonyms":["incompetent","clumsy"],"distractorHint":["有能な","勤勉な","礼儀正しい"]},
