  {"word":"insidious","pos":"adj","ja":"陰険な、じわじわ広がる","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪnˈsɪdiəs","ex":"The disease progresses in a slow, insidious manner.","exJa":"その病気はゆっくりと陰険に進行する。","collocations":["insidious disease","insidious threat"],"synonyms":["subtle","treacherous"],"distractorHint":["明白な","急速な","無害な"]},
  {"word":"instigate","pos":"v","ja":"引き起こす、扇動する","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ˈɪnstɪɡeɪt","ex":"Investigators believe he instigated the riot.","exJa":"捜査官たちは彼が暴動を扇動したと考えている。","collocations":["instigate a riot","instigate change"],"synonyms":["incite","provoke"],"distractorHint":["阻止する","終結させる","目撃する"]},
  {"word":"integral","pos":"adj","ja":"不可欠な、統合された","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ˈɪntɪɡrəl","ex":"Teamwork is integral to the success of this project.","exJa":"チームワークはこの計画の成功に不可欠だ。","collocations":["integral part","integral to"],"synonyms":["essential","fundamental"],"distractorHint":["無関係な","付加的な","一時的な"]},
