  {"word":"intuitive","pos":"adj","ja":"直感的な","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪnˈtuːɪtɪv","ex":"The new app has a very intuitive interface.","exJa":"その新しいアプリは非常に直感的なインターフェースを持つ。","collocations":["intuitive design","intuitive sense"],"synonyms":["instinctive","natural"],"distractorHint":["複雑な","論理的な","不安定な"]},
  {"word":"inundate","pos":"v","ja":"圧倒する、浸水させる","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ˈɪnʌndeɪt","ex":"We were inundated with emails after the announcement.","exJa":"発表後、私たちはメールの山に圧倒された。","collocations":["inundate with requests","be inundated"],"synonyms":["overwhelm","flood"],"distractorHint":["無視する","減らす","乾かす"]},
  {"word":"invoke","pos":"v","ja":"呼び起こす、発動する","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ɪnˈvoʊk","ex":"The government invoked emergency powers during the crisis.","exJa":"政府は危機の間に緊急権限を発動した。","collocations":["invoke a law","invoke a memory"],"synonyms":["cite","summon"],"distractorHint":["廃止する","無効にする","隠す"]},
