  {"word":"jettison","pos":"v","ja":"捨てる、放棄する","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ˈdʒɛtɪsən","ex":"The airline jettisoned its unprofitable routes.","exJa":"その航空会社は不採算路線を切り捨てた。","collocations":["jettison plans","jettison cargo"],"synonyms":["discard","abandon"],"distractorHint":["採用する","保存する","改良する"]},
