  {"word":"juxtapose","pos":"v","ja":"並置する","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ˈdʒʌkstəpoʊz","ex":"The exhibit juxtaposes old photographs with modern art.","exJa":"その展示は古い写真と現代美術を並置している。","collocations":["juxtapose with","juxtaposed against"],"synonyms":["contrast","compare"],"distractorHint":["分離する","混ぜ合わせる","無視する"]},
