  {"word":"lament","pos":"v","ja":"嘆く、悲しむ","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"ləˈmɛnt","ex":"He lamented the loss of the old neighborhood shops.","exJa":"彼は昔ながらの近所の店が失われたことを嘆いた。","collocations":["lament the loss","widely lamented"],"synonyms":["mourn","bemoan"],"distractorHint":["祝う","無視する","期待する"]},
