  {"word":"lax","pos":"adj","ja":"緩い、ずさんな","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"læks","ex":"Security at the old warehouse was surprisingly lax.","exJa":"古い倉庫の警備は驚くほどずさんだった。","collocations":["lax security","lax discipline"],"synonyms":["loose","negligent"],"distractorHint":["厳格な","丁寧な","公正な"]},
